## 9. Feature Coverage Checklist

Every feature from the original brief, mapped to where it lives:

| Original feature | Layer | Notes / change from original |
|------------------|-------|------------------------------|
| Schema-Driven Contextual Canvas | L1 Builder | Uses UI API in *builder* only |
| Implicit Section Repeaters | L1 + L2 | Child-context sections → repeater rows |
| Multi-Page Wizard Layout | L2 | `Page_Number__c` grouping + step validation |
| Dynamic Grid Layouts (1–4 col) | L2 | `Grid_Columns__c` CSS grid |
| Flexible Input Overrides (radio) | L2 | **Reads picklists from snapshot**, not runtime UI API |
| Custom Multi-Select Container | L2 | Pills + checkbox panel; serializes to `a;b;c` |
| Client-Side Logical Visibility | L2 | Field- and section-level |
| Session & URL Autofill | L2 + L3 | **Surface-aware**; `$User` disabled on public |
| Cross-Field Calculation Engine | L2 | Sandboxed evaluator, no `eval` |
| Atomic Cascade DML Handler | L3 shared | **Context-parameterized** (user vs. elevated) |
| Chunked Attachments & Signatures | L2 + L3 | Chunked `ContentVersion`; guest perms via public adapter |
| **Survey mode** | L1 | Same engine; `Form_Type__c = Survey` |
| **External create-records use case** | L3 | Public adapter (Phase 3) |
| **Internal record-page render by Id** | L3 | Record-page adapter (Phase 1) |
| **Screen Flow embed → flow outputs** | L3 | Flow adapter (Phase 2), no DML |

